HEADWORD: Menaion
<hw>Me*na"ion</hw> <pr>(m⟦esl⟧*n⟦amac⟧"y⟦ocr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Menaia</plw> <pr>(-y⟦adot⟧)</pr>.</plu>
<ety>[NL., from Gr. <grk>mhnai^os</grk> monthly.]</ety>
<fld>(Eccl.)</fld> <def>A work of twelve volumes, each containing the
